channel.title: Best (317 server) Has custom Ganodermic,polypore, max cape, death cape etc!
channel.description:
This is a brand new 317 server with alot of fun!
Download client-http://allunitedrsps.webs.com/apps/links/ you need both cache + client to see custom!
Webclient-http://www.rswebclients.com/play/Community%20Rsps
-Forums -http://allunitedrsps.webs.com/
We make sure you dont get bored!
Ivh added some customs link to check them out-http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/35/customse.png/
We have a tokkul shop. Farm tokkul at tzhaar caves-killing higher levels gives more tokkul(Logic)
Pc, modified so you can solo it for those pc points if noone else wants to come with you :( loner
Teampk/instead of kbd. Is a place where people can start pking vs anyone with summoning etc safely. - no rules, yet.
Rest ill post some pics. http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/600/slayershop.png/
http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/14/teampk.png/
